data.name: txtHealPct.ToolTip
data.value: Your toon will try to heal itself when health is at this percent

data.name: txtManaSpam.ToolTip
data.value: Use the spam spell list until mana reaches this percent

data.name: txtCombatWait.ToolTip
data.value: Time, in milliseconds, to wait before restarting combat loop. 0 for no wait. If you are a caster, like a mage or warlock, you might want to set the time lower. For tanks, such as warriors, you might want to set the time higher. 1000 = 1 second

data.name: txtDowntime.ToolTip
data.value: Percent at which mana or health must be before 'downtime' is used. Downtime causes the character to sit. Toon will eat/drink if food/water is available.

data.name: txtPanicThreshold.ToolTip
data.value: Run in panic when the number of attacking mobs is >= this number

data.name: chkDoPanic.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, your bot will check for Panic conditions and act accordingly (checks for too many mobs attacking bot and for health to be too low in combat)

data.name: txtPreCombatBuff.ToolTip
data.value: List of spells to cast to buff your toon or otherwise prepare it before combat (before pulling)

data.name: txtCombatSpam.ToolTip
data.value: List of spells to cast during combat. This list is repeated continuously until combat is finished.

data.name: txtHealingSpell.ToolTip
data.value: Spell to cast to heal yourself during combat

data.name: txtProtectionSpell.ToolTip
data.value: Spell/action to use at the beginning of combat to protect yourself. Stoneskin Totem or Powerword Shield for example

data.name: txtHealingOverTime.ToolTip
data.value: Set to the name of a healing over time spell (or healing stream totem). Used when more than one mob attacks

data.name: txtCombatDOT.ToolTip
data.value: List of DOT spells to cast during combat. These spells are cast once per attacker

data.name: chkSpamRandom.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, combat spam spells are cast ranodmly (not in the order you enter them here). This can make your bot appear more human, although many people prefer a certain casting sequence

data.name: txtPostCombatSpells.ToolTip
data.value: List of spells to cast after combat is finished (before downtime and looting)

data.name: txtStopRunAwayAttempt.ToolTip
data.value: Spell to cast when a mob is attempting to run away from you

data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Drag and Drop spell names into the fields on the right. This is a list of ALL spells for your class. Your toon may not have this spell yet.

data.name: label8.Text
data.value: Stop Attempts to Run Away Spell

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: For each list of spells/actions, put each spell/action to perform on a new line. Leave blank if you don't have/want a spell to cast. Rank is not needed.
